dc_title_s: Map of the original swamp areas of the lower peninsula of Michigan.: 1907. Compiled from John Farmer's map of 1873 for report; by C. A. Davis on peat.
dc_description_s: From Geological Survey of Michigan. Annual report for 1906. Plate XVI. Swamp areas shown in brown. 1 map: col.; 64 x 52 cm. This map is in the public domain. Please attribute access and use of this digitized map to the Stephen S. Clark Library, University of Michigan Library.
